.da KOL1V 21mm 49mm width 85mm
.da KOL1H 112mm 49mm width 85mm
.****** HER LAVES KASSEN RUNDT OM REGLERNE ********************************
.ar SIDE1 on
.bx left right
.sp 235mm
.bx off
